### Get all cars
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars
Accept: application/json

### Check insurance validity for a car (example: carId=1, date=2024-06-01)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/insurance-valid?date=2024-06-01
Accept: application/json

### Test boundary cases for insurance validity check

### Invalid car ID (should return 404)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/999/insurance-valid?date=2024-06-01
Accept: application/json

### Negative car ID (should return 400)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/-1/insurance-valid?date=2024-06-01
Accept: application/json

### Zero car ID (should return 400)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/0/insurance-valid?date=2024-06-01
Accept: application/json

### Invalid date format (should return 400)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/insurance-valid?date=invalid-date
Accept: application/json

### Date too old (should return 400)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/insurance-valid?date=1800-01-01
Accept: application/json

### Date too far in future (should return 400)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/insurance-valid?date=2080-01-01
Accept: application/json

### Create a new car
POST https://localhost:61341/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "vin": "VIN11111111111111",
    "make": "Ford",
    "model": "Focus", 
    "yearOfManufacture": 2022,
    "ownerId": 1
}

### Create car with duplicate VIN (should return 409)
POST https://localhost:61341/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "vin": "VIN12345678901234",
    "make": "Ford",
    "model": "Focus", 
    "yearOfManufacture": 2022,
    "ownerId": 1
}

### Create car with invalid VIN length (should return 400)
POST https://localhost:61341/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "vin": "SHORT",
    "make": "Ford",
    "model": "Focus", 
    "yearOfManufacture": 2022,
    "ownerId": 1
}

### Create insurance policy
POST https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "provider": "NewInsuranceProvider",
    "startDate": "2025-06-01",
    "endDate": "2026-05-31"
}

### Create overlapping insurance policy (should return 409)
POST https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "provider": "OverlapProvider",
    "startDate": "2024-06-01",
    "endDate": "2024-12-31"
}

### Register a claim
POST https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/claims
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "claimDate": "2024-06-15",
    "description": "Minor accident repair",
    "amount": 750.50
}

### Get car history
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/1/history
Accept: application/json

### Get car history for non-existent car (should return 404)
GET https://localhost:61341/api/cars/999/history
Accept: application/json

### Manually trigger policy expiration check (admin endpoint)
POST https://localhost:61341/api/admin/check-expirations
Accept: application/json
